Simple Framework ¯\_(ツ)_/¯

Version: 0.4.2
Author: Thomas Vollath
License: Have fun!
Website: http://monkey-coder.com/framework
Source: https://tomthorgal@github.com/tomthorgal/simple-framework.git

Installation:
==================================================

File: ./header.php
--------------------------------------------------
Replace:
	$base_url = '/framework/';
With:
	$base_url = '{YOUR WEBSITES URL}/';

File: ./css/style.php
--------------------------------------------------
Replace:
	$base_url             = 'http://monkey-coder.com/framework/';
With:
	$base_url             = '{YOUR WEBSITES URL}/';